<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Actually a better way to deal justice</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Lightbringer">Lightbringer</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 6:00 a.m. 13/7/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Actually a better way to deal justice<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2283" TARGET=_self>The naked killers is what gets to me</A> (Lightbringer)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Bieng there will always be those who naked kill people-in alot of cases to fund another char. then mabey there should be a posted board in a town like they have now except you are able to type in the name of the killer and are givin the killers aliases i.e--all of thier chars. names that they use on that particular server-this would allow some absoulutley beautiful pay back that these bare arse people need.

<BR>Think about it-this would place the shoe on the other foot and allow these lamers to be lookin over thier shoulders whether they are there naked lame arse pk or thier high lvl thief or cleric-they are one in the same and should be treated as such.
<BR>I know pking is part of the game and i got no prob with that but i personally would love to be able to know if the guy in me group is the same SOB who waxed me with a DOT spell when i had 20 hitpoints left.
<P>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
